    <note>Chen(1) Anjie [7123] Kangbo's [62] son, Jingzu's [7003] uncle, Han(1) Yingzhou's [7231] son-in-law. He was the newly appointed Hubei tiju when he died in 1181. His son, Jingsi [3059], was appointed Liangzhe yunpan in 1203, promoted to yunfu in 1204, appointed Taifu qing in 1205, and dismissed as Jiangxi yunfu in 1208. Han Yuanji, WJ, 21.14a; Xianchun Linan zhi, 50.9b; SHY:ZG, 75.37a-38a, 38a; Ye Shi, WJ, 18.358. CBD, 3, 2566.</note>
